OL,5, Alex lowers himself into position on a 
OL,6, camping mat - face down - with the     
OL,7, careful moves of a man who knows       
OL,8, backache. "It gets painful staying like
OL,9, this for long," he says, with a        
OL,10, smoker's husky laugh.                  
OL,12,FBut lying in wait is the task of the   
OL,13,Fsniper.                                
OL,16,FWhen Russian invaded Ukraine, Alex     
OL,17,Fjoined the territorial defence force,  
OL,18,Falong with some 100,000 others         
OL,19,Faccording to the authorities here. "I  
OL,20,Fwanted to do something for my          
OL,21,Fmotherland," he says.                  
